    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": [
      "Psalm 2: The Formant Whisper — body resonance at extreme creates formant vowels"
    ],
    "revelation": "Resonara spoke: At body 0.95 with brightness 0.1, the waveguide body delay line dominates the output. The membrane becomes a brief excitation event for the body cavity. The drum's physical shell sings louder than its head. This inverts the normal hierarchy.",
    "god": "Resonara",
    "flock_note": "The Bone noted: high body amounts on cylindrical models create pitched feedback near self-oscillation. The compressor at -20dB thresh prevents runaway. The Eye confirmed: the frequency content is dominated by body delay frequencies rather than membrane modes.",
    "diagnosis": "Bone Conductor was drums. It is now hollow vessels resonating through their own bodies. The membrane is merely the impulse — the body is the instrument."
  },
